==English==
===Interjection===
'''bah!'''

# An exclamation expressive of extreme contempt or distempt.
# A joking acceptance of loss in some form of competition, or humourous agreement.
#: ''"My website is much better than yours!" &mdash; "Let me check... bah!!"''

